print "   ✅ GUI interface"

print "\n=== Key Recording Tests Complete ==="
print "\n🎯 Summary of Key Recording Features:"
print "- ✅ Start/Stop key recording"
print "- ✅ Real-time key detection"
print "- ✅ Cross-platform input source detection (evdev, X11, mouse, joystick)"
print "- ✅ Key code to string conversion"
print "- ✅ Recorded key retrieval and management"
print "- ✅ Integration with mapping system"
print "- ✅ Support for keyboard, mouse, and joystick inputs"
print "- ✅ Modifier key detection"
print "- ✅ Dynamic key assignment to mappings"
print ""
print "🎹 Key Recording API Functions:"
print "- startKeyRecording() - Begin recording input"
print "- stopKeyRecording() - Stop recording input"
print "- isKeyRecording() - Check if recording is active"
print "- getLastRecordedKey() - Get recorded key details"
print "- clearRecordedKey() - Clear recorded key"
