print "- detectInputSource(keyCode) - Detect input source type"
print "- keyCodeToString(keyCode, source) - Convert code to readable string"
print ""
print "🎮 Recording Workflow:"
print "1. User clicks 'Record Key' button in GUI"
print "2. System starts recording (mapmanager.startKeyRecording())"
print "3. User presses any key/button/move/joystick input"
print "4. System detects and records the input"
print "5. System stops recording (mapmanager.stopKeyRecording())"
